<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Hugo on Darkblue Soul</title><link>https://www.darkbluesoul.cc/categories/hugo/</link><description>Recent content in Hugo on Darkblue Soul</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 09 May 2022 07:57:10 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.darkbluesoul.cc/categories/hugo/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>适用于hugo-theme-stack的微博icon</title><link>https://www.darkbluesoul.cc/p/%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8Ehugo-theme-stack%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9Aicon/</link><pubDate>Mon, 09 May 2022 07:57:10 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.darkbluesoul.cc/p/%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8Ehugo-theme-stack%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9Aicon/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://www.darkbluesoul.cc/p/%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8Ehugo-theme-stack%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9Aicon/weibo-icon.png" alt="Featured image of post 适用于hugo-theme-stack的微博icon" />&lt;p>总觉得社交资料页没有微博好像少了点什么，网上的图标大多是填充的，修改了颜色放上去也觉得不好看。
那就自己整个呗，找了&lt;a class="link" href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_42247720/article/details/120807255" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>qq、微信、微博的svg小图标&lt;/a>，修改了一下，算是满意了。&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="新建微博图标">新建微博图标&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>新建文件，复制以下代码，保存到assets/icons/brand-weibo.svg。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-svg" data-lang="svg">&lt;span class="nt">&amp;lt;svg&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">xmlns=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">width=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;24&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">height=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;24&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">viewBox=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;0 0 24 24&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">stroke-width=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;2&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">stroke=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;currentColor&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">fill=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;none&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">stroke-linecap=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;round&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">stroke-linejoin=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;round&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="nt">&amp;lt;path&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">class=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;st0&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="na">d=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;M10,20.4c-3.9,0-8-1.9-8-5.1c0-1.7,1.1-3.6,2.9-5.3c3.7-3.7,7.6-3.7,6.5-0.2c-0.3,0.5,0.4,0.2,0.4,0.2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s"> c3-1.3,5.2-0.6,4.2,1.9c-0.1,0.4,0,0.4,0.3,0.5C21.3,14,17.6,20.4,10,20.4L10,20.4z M18.7,10c1.3-3.9-3-3.6-3-3.3 M21.7,10.5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s"> c1.9-7.5-6-7.6-6.2-6.6&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">/&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="nt">&amp;lt;/svg&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="修改站点配置">修改站点配置&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>修改config.yaml,在&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 5
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 6
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 7
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 8
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt"> 9
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">10
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">11
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">12
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="nt">social&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">identifier&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">github&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">GitHub&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">url&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">https://github.com/yourID&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">params&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">icon&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">brand-github&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="nt">identifier&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">twitter&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">Twitter&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">url&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">https://twitter.com/yourID&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">params&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">icon&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">brand-twitter&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>下面增加&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
